attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection
Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: This historic home seamlessly blends historical elegance w/ modern charm. Upon entry, you are greeted by a curved mahogany staircase. 1st floor boasts a gourmet kitchen w/ quartz countertops, an oversized island, stainless steel appliances, cherry cabinets, original arches & 10' ceilings. The grand living room features a marble fireplace & powder bath. 2nd floor offers 2 king-size bedrooms, 1 w/ marble fireplace & custom built-in cabinets, a walk-in closet & full bathroom w/ an oversized shower & bench seating. The top floor includes 2 additional queen-size bedrooms, 1 w/ a walk-in closet & the other w/ partial views of downtown. The finished basement adds extra living space w/ built-ins, a full-size W/D, full bathroom & mudroom w/ built-ins leading to the backyard. Outside, enjoy a 3,500 sq. ft. lot w/ a 2-tiered stone patio, custom gas fire pit, benches & beautiful stone walls—perfect for entertaining. The enormous yard is fenced with a grass area & a Reeds Ferry shed for storage.

exclusions: Large Mirror In The Entry Way.
